text: Ondřej Uherka (born 24 September 1991 in Uherské Hradiště) is a Czech professional squash player. As of February 2018, he was ranked number 133 in the world. He is in the Czech Republic men's national squash team. ==References== Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male squash players Category:People from Uherské Hradiště
